#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "Term Image Block"
msgstr "Term-Bild-Block"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Display taxonomy term images with automatic detection and manual selection."
msgstr ""
"Zeigt Taxonomie-Term-Bilder mit automatischer Erkennung und manueller "
"Auswahl an."

#. Author of the plugin
msgid "Carsten Bach"
msgstr "Carsten Bach"

